title: The Developer or the Owner submitting the Scheme will submit it in the Form and the Annexure prescribed along with all relevant documents to the C
clause_text: The Developer or the Owner submitting the Scheme will submit it in the Form and the Annexure prescribed along with all relevant documents to the C.E.O., S.R.A. Forms and Annexure prescribed by the C.E.O. shall be made available to the Registered Developer / Owner on payment of fees as decided by C.E.O., S.R.A. Pune.
